title: Euphemia 25-004(3)
description: An elegant satin mermaid wedding dress featuring a lace-up back, adorned with 3D floral lace delicately scattered throughout. The dress includes a detachable long train and dropped voluminous sleeves with pleats, also embellished with the same intricate lace.

title: Boudica 25-005(3)
description: A luxurious satin A-line dress with an exquisite sweetheart corset featuring pleats and adorned with pearls. The dress transforms into a completely different ensemble with a detachable bolero made of delicate lace, featuring a high neckline, decorated with 3D flowers, and buttons down the back.

title: Amina 25-006(3)
description: A mermaid silhouette gown with a dropped waistline, crafted from lace adorned with sequins and beads. The dress features removable thin beaded straps and detachable sleeves. The gown is complemented by a lace-up back and a long, elegant train.

title: Isolde 25-007(3)
description: An elegant, form-fitting gown made of satin, featuring a draped corset and a straight neckline. It has removable triple straps adorned with 3D flowers and beads, and is complemented by an elegant train and a lace-up back.

title: Blanche 25-008(3)
description: A stylish, sleek gown that hugs the hips and flares at the bottom, crafted from satin and delicate lace. The dress features a removable lace-up corset, with stitched lines that accentuate the curves of the body.

title: Noor 25-009(3)
description: An extraordinary mermaid silhouette gown made of satin, distinguished by its unique corset shape adorned with pearl embellishments that gracefully highlight the bust. The back of the dress features draping that flows into an elegant train. A remarkable decoration that complements the gown is a pearl necklace that cascades over the shoulders, creating an absolutely stunning look.

title: Margrethe 25-010(3)
description: An A-line gown with a sweetheart neckline, crafted from sugar taffeta and lace with 3D appliqus and a zipper back. The dress features removable long sleeves and a detachable lace neck decoration, and is complemented by a royal train.

title: Lucretia 25-011(3)
description: A fairytale A-line gown crafted from luxurious Mikado fabric, featuring a straight neckline. The dress is adorned with delicate straps made of Mikado and organza flowers, adding a touch of elegance. A high slit on the leg completes this enchanting look.

title: Hera 25-012(3)
description: Dreamy satin wedding gown adorned with embroidered lace on the corset that extends onto the sides of the dress. The back of the dress features a lace-up design and a luxurious train. Complementing the gown are removable mesh sleeve gloves, decorated with the same exquisite lace as the dress.

title: Faustina 25-014(3)
description: Dreamy off-the-shoulder satin wedding dress in ivory colour with a heart-shaped neckline, draped bodice, and an open back with lace-up closure. Features a full skirt with a very long train.

title: Aelia 25-015(3)
description: Statement mermaid gown made from luxurious Italian satin, featuring a removable architectural-style embellishment adorned with 3D flowers along the back, cascading into a delicate mesh train. The form-fitting silhouette boasts a sweetheart neckline and a fitted maxi skirt with an elegant train.

title: Matilda 25-001(3)
description: A luxurious satin princess dress with an unusual heart-shaped corset, stitched with expressive lines and 3D flower applique that seem to bloom from within. An unusual decor is also the basque on the sides of the waist. The long train dress is ideally combined with detachable sleeves, decorated with the same delicate lace, creating an elegant look.

title: Carmen 25-002(3)
description: Off-the-shoulder princess dress crafted in sumptuous taffeta, featuring a long train. The gown presents a heart-shaped neckline, embellished with 3D flowers. The skirt is adorned with voluminous ruffles and a daring leg slit. Lacing at the back ensures a flattering fit, and a floral neck accessorie adds a finishing touch of sophistication to the look.

title: Eleanor 25-003(3)
description: Elegant mermaid satin gown with intricate pearl pattern on the sides of the dress. Paired with a removable mesh cape and pearl necklace that matches the dress's design, the look exudes luxurious allure.
